"{\"uid\": \"nbcnewyork.com-paris-2024-summer-olympics-simone-biles-wins-gold-womens-vault-finals-paris-olympics-jade-carey-5665154\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The American women's gymnastics team may have won gold for the team all-around, but the Team USA stars rallied around Simone Biles to celebrate her fifth Olympic gold medal.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9985509321149093, \"rank\": 0.0014506793425543402, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone Bileswon the gold medal inthe women's vault finalsatthe Paris Olympics, once again drilling a Yurchenko double pike and putting a bigger exclamation point on her title as the \\\"Greatest Of All Time.\\\"\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 238, \"end\": 252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a red leotard the NBC commentators called her \\\"power color,\\\" Biles showed why she's the best there is in the sport.\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On her first vault, she once again performedher new signature skill, the Yurchenko double pike, officially named the 'Biles II' in the sport's Code of Points.\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 574, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"score\": 0.9924615128803714, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yurchenko\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She earned a 15.700 for her effort on that first vault and then a 14.900 on her second vault, for a total score of 15.300, and handing Biles the vault gold again, which she last took home in the 2016 Rio Olympics.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch NBC 4 free wherever you are  She had tough competition, especially fromBrazil's Rebeca Andrade, who took the gold medal at the 2020 Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 1029, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebeca Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andrade took home the silver medal with a final score of 14.966 and the United States' Jade Carey took home the bronze with a score of 14.466.\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1031, \"end\": 1038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.999999655010984, \"rank\": 3.4498460347698673e-07, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}, {\"begin\": 1103, \"end\": 1116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9994718599868357, \"rank\": 0.0005009868079100186, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jade Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles now has 10 Olympics medals, including seven golds, one silver, and two bronze.\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1259, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's the most-decorated American gymnast of all time and just keeps adding to her legacy.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1285, \"end\": 1293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9985509321149093, \"rank\": 0.0014506793425543402, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch all the action from the Paris Olympic and Paralympic Games live on Peacock  Biles is not done in Paris either.\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1382, \"end\": 1387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.99999996147426, \"rank\": 3.852594528121016e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1425, \"end\": 1432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999978574669728, \"rank\": 2.142221580416619e-06, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}, {\"begin\": 1455, \"end\": 1460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.99999996147426, \"rank\": 3.852594528121016e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's expected to compete in the balance beam and floor finals on Monday.\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"YOUR OLYMPIC VAULT CHAMPION \\ud83e\\udd47@Simone_Bilesis golden again!#ParisOlympicspic.twitter.com/3RQlFph9wA  Simone Biles had a total score of 15.300 in the women's vault finals.\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1713, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1645, \"end\": 1657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In her first vault, Biles scored a 15.700, including a difficulty score of 6.400, an execution score of 9.400, and a penalty of -0.1.\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In her second vault, Biles scored a 14.900, including a difficulty score of 5.600 and an execution score of 9.300.\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1964, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MAKE THAT 7\\ufe0f\\u20e3!\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@Simone_Bilestakes home her seventh Olympic Gold Medal with a victory on Vault at the Paris Games!\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2078, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83d\\udc10pic.twitter.com/utgqy5nFwZ  Here's how the gymnasts scored in the women's vault finals (in order of performance):  Gymnasts perform two vaults with their scores averaged together for the total score.\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The gymnast with the highest average score for their two vaults in the finals wins.\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The women's vault final will reair on 'Primetime in Paris' on NBC, Peacock andstreaming on NBCOlympics.comSaturday at 8 p.m.\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2420, \"end\": 2425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.99999996147426, \"rank\": 3.852594528121016e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2435, \"end\": 2442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999978574669728, \"rank\": 2.142221580416619e-06, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ET on Saturday, Aug. 3.\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2514, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The GOAT is golden again.\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83e\\udd47Simone Biles is the#ParisOlympicsvault champion.\\ud83d\\udcfa NBC, E!\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2546, \"end\": 2558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"and Peacockpic.twitter.com/XpyHqaQpGu  Simone Biles led the qualifiers with a score of 15.300.\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2695, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brazil's Rebeca Andrade qualified with a score of 14.683.\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2700, \"end\": 2706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8872230560740867, \"rank\": 0.09523284932116775, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2700, \"end\": 2706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8872230560740867, \"rank\": 0.09523284932116775, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2709, \"end\": 2723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebeca Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"U.S. gymnast Jade Carey qualified third with a score of 14.333.\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2763, \"end\": 2770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7264648454301075e-13, \"text\": \"gymnast\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\"}, {\"begin\": 2771, \"end\": 2781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jade Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's the full list of qualifiers for the women's vault final:  Jordan Chiles ranked fourth in qualifying, but due to the two competitors per country rule, she is not able to compete in the final.\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 3016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2874, \"end\": 2885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics_\\u2013_Women's_vault\", \"score\": 0.6166663945842508, \"rank\": 0.32915057915055035, \"text\": \"vault final\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics_\\u2013_Women's_vault\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics_\\u2013_Women's_vault\"}, {\"begin\": 2888, \"end\": 2901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gymnasts are scored by two panels on the content and execution of their routine.\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3098, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Perfect total scores no longer come to a value of 10, though gymnasts can get a perfect 10 for execution.\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3205, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Scores typically fall in the 14- to 16-point range.\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Total scoresare based on the total of the difficulty score and execution score combined, minus any deductions.\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The difficulty panel decides the \\\"D-score\\\" while the execution panel starts at 10.0 and deducts points based on how the routine went.\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The execution score is the \\\"e-score.\\\"\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's the D-score plus the E-score minus Deductions to get the total score.\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Deductions or penalties can occur if a gymnast goes out of bounds.\", \"from\": 3622, \"to\": 3688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gymnasts can lose anywhere from 0.1 points for something small that happened during the routine to 1.0 point for a fall.\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The difficulty score is based on \\\"difficulty, connection value and element requirements\\\" and the execution score, which includes \\\"execution, artistry, composition and technique,\\\"according to our partners at NBC Olympics.\", \"from\": 3811, \"to\": 4031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4022, \"end\": 4034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The official rule book is the FIG Code of Points.\", \"from\": 4033, \"to\": 4082, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MyKayla Skinner won the silver medal in the 2020 Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 4084, \"to\": 4148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4088, \"end\": 4103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MyKayla_Skinner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"MyKayla Skinner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MyKayla_Skinner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MyKayla_Skinner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles won the gold in Rio in the 2016 Olympics.\", \"from\": 4150, \"to\": 4204, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aug. 4 - Women's uneven bar final: The women's uneven bars final begins at 9 a.m. ET/6 a.m. PT on Sunday, Aug 4 on NBC and Peacock.\", \"from\": 4206, \"to\": 4337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4333, \"end\": 4340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999978574669728, \"rank\": 2.142221580416619e-06, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aug. 5 - Women's balance beam finals: The women's balance beam finals begins at 6:36 a.m. ET/3:36 a.m. PT on Monday, Aug. 5.\", \"from\": 4339, \"to\": 4463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The event will air on E!\", \"from\": 4464, \"to\": 4488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"and Peacock.\", \"from\": 4489, 